OL,3,CToxic legacy: Why is Britain behind
OL,4,CEurope in tackling DES scandal?
OL,6,FIt was meant to prevent miscarriages,
OL,7,Fbut instead left behind a devastating
OL,8,Ftrail of rare cancers, infertility,
OL,9,Ftraumatic births and lifelong
OL,10,Fcomplications for the children of the
OL,11,Fwomen who took it.
OL,13,FUnlike in other countries such as the
OL,14,FNetherlands and the United States,
OL,15,Fwhere victims have secured
OL,16,Fcompensation, specialist healthcare
OL,17,Fand enhanced cancer screenings, the
OL,18,FBritish families affected say they
OL,19,Fhave been left abandoned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
