OL,3,CToxic legacy: Why is Britain behind
OL,4,CEurope in tackling DES scandal?
OL,6,FThis summer, I travelled to the
OL,7,FNetherlands to find out how those
OL,8,Fexposed to DES have won important
OL,9,Fvictories in their fight for
OL,10,Frecognition of the harm done, and what
OL,11,Fthe UK could learn from their approach.
OL,13,FWatch ITV's Tonight programme Toxic
OL,14,FLegacy: Our Hidden Drug Scandal at
OL,15,F8.30pm on September 11, on ITV1 and
OL,16,FITVX.
