OL,3,CToxic legacy: Why is Britain behind
OL,4,CEurope in tackling DES scandal?
OL,6,FIt took decades of campaigning, legal
OL,7,Farguments and many setbacks, but Dutch
OL,8,FDES survivors finally got a stunning
OL,9,Fvictory in the early 2000s.
OL,11,FSix DES daughters started the first
OL,12,Fcourt case in the 1980s against ten
OL,13,Fdrug companies, which was then
OL,14,Fdismissed by the courts because the
OL,15,Fwomen couldn't prove which
OL,16,Fmanufacturer supplied the DES
OL,17,Fprescribed to their mothers.
OL,19,FDES was never patented and was made by
OL,20,Fmore than 200 companies globally,
OL,21,Fmaking it difficult to prove.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
