OL,3,CToxic legacy: Why is Britain behind
OL,4,CEurope in tackling DES scandal?
OL,6,FIn 2007, Ingrid Seeboldt became one of
OL,7,Fthe first Dutch DES daughters to
OL,8,Freceive a financial settlement. Her
OL,9,Fmother was given the drug while three
OL,10,Fmonths pregnant.
OL,12,FAs a teenager, Ingrid was treated for
OL,13,Fclear-cell adenocarcinoma (CCA), the
OL,14,Frare cancer linked to DES exposure,
OL,15,Fand the treatment left her unable to
OL,16,Fhave children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
