OL,6,F"I think the mental harm was bigger
OL,7,Fwith me than the physical harm, I felt
OL,8,Fso alone," she told me at her home
OL,9,Foutside Amsterdam. "I think I would be
OL,10,Fa wonderful mother, a very good
OL,11,Fmother. It still hurts, it's
OL,12,Funbelievable."
OL,14,FIngrid received more than E120,000 in
OL,15,Fcompensation, one of the largest
OL,16,Fpayouts on a scale measuring the
OL,17,Fdamage caused by the drug.
