OL,3,CToxic legacy: Why is Britain behind
OL,4,CEurope in tackling DES scandal?
OL,6,FAt Maastricht University Hospital, I
OL,7,Fmet Dr Brigitte Slangen, a DES
OL,8,Fspecialist doctor who provides expert
OL,9,Fcare for the daughters of women given
OL,10,Fthe drug.
OL,12,F"The generational impact is enormous,"
OL,13,FDr Slangan told ITV's Tonight.
OL,15,F"It was prescribed to a lot of women
OL,16,Fwho were pregnant, and the children of
OL,17,Fthose women developed the cancers,
OL,18,Fthey got the problems, and the
OL,19,Fchildren of those children ... we are
OL,20,Fnot really sure when it stops."
