OL,6,FSocial Affairs Correspondent Sarah
OL,7,FCorker travelled to the Netherlands
OL,8,Fwith the ITV Tonight programme to find
OL,9,Fout more about the Dutch approach to
OL,10,FDES screenings and compensation
OL,12,FShe recalled how, when evidence
OL,13,Femerged of DES-related harm, one of
OL,14,Fthe first things that happened was a
OL,15,Fhuge effort to trace and inform the
OL,16,Ffirst and second generations of women
OL,17,Fexposed to it.
