OL,6,FA process involving trawling through
OL,7,Fmedical records to ascertain the scale
OL,8,Fof the problem. Something that never
OL,9,Fhappened in the UK, and would be
OL,10,Fimpossible to do today, as medical
OL,11,Frecords proving who was prescribed DES
OL,12,Fhave been destroyed or lost.
OL,14,FUsage of DES in Europe varied country
OL,15,Fby country, but at least half a
OL,16,Fmillion pregnancies are thought to
OL,17,Fhave been exposed to the drug. In the
OL,18,FNetherlands, it's estimated to be as
