OL,6,FIn the UK, there have been no
OL,7,Fsuccessful cases, but campaigners are
OL,8,Fnow considering legal action.
OL,10,FClare Fletcher, partner at law firm
OL,11,FBroudie Jackson Canter, who is
OL,12,Frepresenting UK victims, told ITV News
OL,13,Fthere needs to be a full-scale public
OL,14,Finquiry into how a drug this harmful
OL,15,Fwas handed out so freely and to help
